Coerce to a tibble or data frame

Coerce to a tibble or data frame

# S3 method for tbl_ts
as_tibble(x, ...)

# S3 method for tbl_ts
as.data.frame(x, ...)

Arguments

x

A tbl_ts.
...

Ignored.

Examples

as_tibble(pedestrian)
#> # A tibble: 66,071 x 5
#>    Sensor                        Date_Time           Date        Time Count

# a grouped tbl_ts -----
grped_ped <- pedestrian %>% group_by(Sensor)
as_tibble(grped_ped)
#> # A tibble: 66,071 x 5
#> # Groups:   Sensor [4]
#>    Sensor                        Date_Time           Date        Time Count
